  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-553dd96c-d5fc-4954-aba9-e6ffbcbc6d26\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-03231a54-424d-4d0d-85de-33b5db824c3f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1e0d7f71-ec7b-4401-8704-54c569127181\"><span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#클림트</span></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-71dbec51-f51f-492b-b4d8-5721066ca3aa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-badaebd2-ba97-46b4-a67f-7d5c8a4cdc7a\">5월에 제주도에 갔었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0d13be2d-3601-45e9-8ce3-8a3c359e5aae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6cf43a2f-97c3-4e1e-88fd-5aa2ff4701f1\">지인들도 만날겸 겸사겸사 갔었는데, 여행과 관련한 목표는 단 한가지 &#x27;빛의 벙커&#x27;를 방문하기 였습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a895f220-8aae-4efa-ad2e-7389a1c98766\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0bd4db65-fb43-44b5-8d60-a0414feafd2e\">이미 지인들에게서 좋았다는 경험담을 많이 들었기에 기대가 컸습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6e9c2538-bfa6-47f3-b1f1-65d38a9ecc79\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b4297e10-46df-498e-a53f-7fcbdef1d09b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-de2337d8-3901-45cb-9a2b-82a58bb00bee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9db3ea8c-addf-4d9b-a21d-c2d9242b0587\">현재 제주도 빛의 벙커는 클림트를 main으로 전시 중. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6dc7247-735a-4a91-8815-75b051d29023\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c6dc7247-735a-4a91-8815-75b051d29023\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/834f3e88b8d22e0f.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/834f3e88b8d22e0f.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/834f3e88b8d22e0f.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"666\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e0feeac7-fb72-41ff-95f6-0feacc36d74a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b5822e5d-ce30-4d54-9fe3-ebd9ae8f091c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0e137805-cb01-4fc8-88ab-84ffde3126d5\">처음 접하는 새로운 형식의 전시형태라 아주~ 감동깊게 관람을 했죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n